{"tid":2073490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熱狗泰回應連登仔：你們繼續玩泛民小圈子抹黑吧，我認真做事，我相信有識之士是會看到的。","createTime":"2020-06-21T11:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T13:51:37.000Z","uid":131282,"like":10,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8960f8bea42bee0b7667c8a9ebda7e1bd24fa7de","tid":2073490,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:17:04.000Z","msg":"熱血公民蟲太：每每泛民做壞事，熱狗總會被抹黑老屈，其手法千篇一律。<br />\n<br />\n日前街工不服從初選協定，其他泛民大佬以退出初選機制迫使梁耀忠退選，導致「泛民初選分化泛民」的局面；今日連登就出現抹黑熱狗的帖文，指【街工主席原來係一隻熱狗】。<br />\n<br />\n然而我寫此帖不是為「罵戰」，因為我對這個話題完全沒有興趣，在34度的烈日下，參與這個「討論」的人的腦袋可以扭出水來。<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家懂得欣賞我們怎樣做實事，並請你介紹熱狗給你的朋友，勸勉大家珍惜同道中人。<br />\n<br />\n該帖有一個觀察，指梁耀忠議員與我常常一同開記招。這個觀察沒錯，不過說得不夠，要我加以補充：<br />\n<br />\n在農曆年後，有經營私營補習中心的校監與我聯絡，表示接到教育局的指令，要求補習社停課停業，希望我能夠提供協助；但由於疫情未明，我只給了一些建議，並未有公開表示跟進。<br />\n<br />\n其後，教育中心聯盟的負責人再與我聯絡，指梁耀忠議員願意協助他們召開記招，並詢問我會否介意，如果可能的話，更希望我可以仗義參與。<br />\n<br />\n結果我答應了，原因非常簡單，能夠幫助業界，我便去做。在此期間，我在背後做了什麼，並不重要；重要的，是為私補界從教育局那裡爭取一個公道。<br />\n<br />\n你們繼續玩泛民小圈子抹黑吧，我認真做事，我相信有識之士是會看到的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LnEGhzP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLnEGhzP.jpg&h=6fcf366f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蟲太同白頭佬一齊開記招仲唔係鬼？理撚得你咪係做實事幫人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093cbf55be9569adce7136646a0e84466eac9a9e","tid":2073490,"uid":66798,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:21:41.000Z","msg":"反熱狗就係「泛粉」？<br />\n<br />\n蟲泰口中班左膠都成日屈本土派「熱狗」，熱狗同左膠水平未又一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6c1ab1a53149e9d028dc6097dce16b89c3d6b2","tid":2073490,"uid":269202,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:22:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得你純粹係靠鬧泛民搵市場，你話你做野<br />\n<br />\n我認為而家最需要做係贏選舉同推動國際線<br />\n<br />\n而你同旗下宣傳隊，係做緊私怨定係實事<br />\n<br />\n你懂的"},{"pid":"16dcea6f1f9955477b9af08a02b8047cc75e1578","tid":2073490,"uid":9710,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:32:01.000Z","msg":"好後悔四年前投左比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e52902837524b082d324f1878a9cb2cb05426e1","tid":2073490,"uid":4564,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"16dcea6f1f9955477b9af08a02b8047cc75e1578","tid":2073490,"uid":9710,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:32:01.000Z","msg":"好後悔四年前投左比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:34:48.000Z","msg":"人生污點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1a9e3fef6a219ca454bc7f2fe8755da8edccb4","tid":2073490,"uid":67813,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:35:26.000Z","msg":"其實佢選乜撚野？<br />\n熱狗唔係話退出社運既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5f678068b06429efb089c00f05d70b2ef2c8cd","tid":2073490,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:39:21.000Z","msg":"成日講做野<br />\n其實佢地做左啲咁野咁巴閉<br />\n<br />\n（4年前投四眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"2f78c599b01b62757315401dbfe5c71ec2d704a9","tid":2073490,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:39:49.000Z","msg":"發現泰博唔聽國師話鳩戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要投白票了"},{"pid":"d614d07607f545bac0eaa52250076cb3b8e2534f","tid":2073490,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:40:25.000Z","msg":"熱狗+白頭佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dbd81d74719e915c0a4f4787d9aab719dbfbc62","tid":2073490,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:40:59.000Z","msg":"唔支持熱狗既人一定係犯聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b13266a7349bd6f941773b509222804427f371","tid":2073490,"uid":55571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:45:16.000Z","msg":"佢嘅論點就係<br />\n你應該睇到我做過咩<br />\n除非你係豬<br />\n而唔係講自己做過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和你唔係勇你無勇過泛民你又杯<br />\n用消錯法只能係民建聯B隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f18bd185741ec16693e9ffba873e65f77d5a3a5","tid":2073490,"uid":238370,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:57:28.000Z","msg":"收皮啦反骨仔！入到閘你照樣輸！"},{"pid":"0a972f937bf44dfb3aa3754348734ed26b14a6f9","tid":2073490,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:01:15.000Z","msg":"鳩坐泰同以前班老坑泛民一鳩樣垃圾"},{"pid":"35e612aa35055088a8753e9fd134c2e3acd9d4c4","tid":2073490,"uid":231908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:07:34.000Z","msg":"撐熱血街工#heh<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f90994cbf2c4553dfedf28794fd52846b3b6427","tid":2073490,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:08:59.000Z","msg":"iq test"},{"pid":"1232ef45fc0fc405738d1f0da7b432aae1be597c","tid":2073490,"uid":337899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:09:53.000Z","msg":"熱血街工民"},{"pid":"550f6df9c03c8b997e05e5f63141f15e02e12f4e","tid":2073490,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:11:37.000Z","msg":"背叛完本土派仲想扮本土"},{"pid":"6ba08c7949d3413df9972468298c043f996a5e15","tid":2073490,"uid":240606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:47:20.000Z","msg":"泰生呢四年除咗插央，有冇人話我知佢做過乜嘢？"},{"pid":"37dc8b9c7c0f84a0bd666a080def161467d2796a","tid":2073490,"uid":29130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:48:22.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好再轉隻熱狗D野上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWFC"},{"pid":"afed41d8114a0e3c7011155746c674ea14d32957","tid":2073490,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:08:07.000Z","msg":"最撚憎熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n垃圾泛民都好撚過熱狗"},{"pid":"c8a53fca1025c319a3d33f38cd7324fa0e51ba8a","tid":2073490,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:09:59.000Z","msg":"屌票，熱狗正常發揮，票喺你哋手吧。"},{"pid":"9b1547048e9e80806c709e0fdfd1f894f81ffc43","tid":2073490,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:23:10.000Z","msg":"蟲泰坐低.jpg"},{"pid":"93c5e73e8184e5ac50343fc1527b2bf1a7e09f77","tid":2073490,"uid":62314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:39:06.000Z","msg":"我一票松泰 一票白頭佬，四年後我屌晒你地兩個老母"},{"pid":"e86c4f3d7338ac6703b0adc780df1d0ccc653165","tid":2073490,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩四年前都無投俾呢班垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d8a3551c60198fe4cf94374838e8576bda05c9","tid":2073490,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e52902837524b082d324f1878a9cb2cb05426e1","tid":2073490,"uid":4564,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"16dcea6f1f9955477b9af08a02b8047cc75e1578","tid":2073490,"uid":9710,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:32:01.000Z","msg":"好後悔四年前投左比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:34:48.000Z","msg":"人生污點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:43:15.000Z","msg":"我都有人生污點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}